---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<Layout title="Chelsea Avery">
  <div>
    <main>
      <Header
        title="Chelsea Avery"
        subtitle="Software Developer"
        github={{
          text: "GitHub",
          href: "https://github.com/chelseaerinavery",
        }}
        blueSky={{
          text: "Bluesky",
          href: "https://bsky.app/profile/chelsea-avery.com",
        }}
        linkedIn={{
          text: "LinkedIn",
          href: "https://www.linkedin.com/in/chelseaavery/",
        }}
      />
      <div class="bio-wrapper">
        <section>
          <p>
            Hi, I’m Chelsea, a full-stack software developer and “Jill of
            Abundant Trades” based in Boulder, CO. I’m currently contributing to
            the front end of
            <a
              href="https://weedmaps.com"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">Weedmaps</a
            >, where I help build accessible, responsive web applications using
            React, TypeScript, and Next.js. I love learning new things and
            finding my flow state. I'm especially passionate about the
            intersection of usability, reliability, and accessibility. I love
            data almost as much as I love design.
          </p><p>
            Outside of work, I'm currently:
            <ul>
              <li>
                Working on Mosh Hamedani's "The Ultimate React Native Series."
              </li>
              <li>
                Exploring the craft of agentic engineering, both personally and
                professionally.
              </li>
              <li>
                Fostering a friendly tech community at <a
                  href="https://bouldertechconnect.com"
                  target="_blank">Boulder Tech Connect</a
                > ✨
              </li>
            </ul>
          </p>
        </section>
        <p></p>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .bio-wrapper {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .bio-wrapper a {
    text-decoration: underline;
    color: #42406a;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .bio-wrapper a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
    color: #0da64f;
  }
</style>
